{
    "a_galaxy_workflow": "true",
    "annotation": "This workflow extracts 5 different time periods e.g. January- June 2019, 2020 and 2021, July-December 2019 and 2020 over a single selected location. Then statistics (mean, minimum, maximum) are computed. The final products are maximum, minimum and mean.",
